chip
Homonym Number: 2
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:short for <i>chip basket</i>,a small container, formerly of thin strips of wood, for holding berries and other soft fruit. In NZ earlier called punnet, or strawberry-box; now, occas. and esp. plastic, a pottle
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes:
